CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, July 26, 1958, pg. B5 reads: " Scholarship Recipients - These young men and women were recipients of scholarships given by the Metoka Club at its annual scholarship garden party, July 17... - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of four women, including one on left wearing light colored dress, beaded necklace, and light colored hat, holding documents in front of three young women wearing "scholarship" ribbons, standing in front of Lemington Avenue Home for Aged Women for Metoka Club garden party, another version
